{"title":"2024 iPad Air: Everything you need to know about the new iPad Air M2","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2110304/ipad-air-2024-release-date-specs-display-size-price-processor.html","date":1715099134000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>Apple has updated the iPad Air for 2024 at an event which Apple CEO Tim Cook described as the “Biggest day for iPad”. The new iPad Pro comes in two sizes: 11 inch and 13 inch, features the M2 chip, and much more. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>iPad Air M2 release date </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Apple unveiled two new iPad Air models at an event on May 7, 2024. Pre-orders started immediately following the event and the new products will ship on Wednesday May 15.</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=1-1-2110304-7-0-0&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/buy-ipad/ipad-air\" target=\"_blank\">Order the iPad Air from Apple here</a></p>\n\n\n<h2>iPad Air M2 Prices </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The new 11-inch iPad Air for 2024 starts at $599/£599. The new 13-inch iPad Air starts at $799/£799.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new 11-inch and 13-inch iPad Air will be available in 256GB, 512GB and 1TB configurations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For education, the new 11-inch iPad Air starts at $549 and the 13-inch model starts at $749. U.K. education prices to be confirmed. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>iPad Air M2 Design </h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"iPad Air 2024 color options\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2360w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=768%2C430&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.