or options\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2360w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=768%2C430&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=1200%2C671&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=1536%2C859&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=2048%2C1145&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-hero.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"671\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the first time Apple has added an additional size to the iPad Air line up. The iPad Air will now be available in 11-inch and 13-inch configurations. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apple described the new 13-inch model as offering 30 percent more screen real estate than the 11-inch model. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both models will feature the same screen technology. A Liquid Retina display with anti-reflective screen coating; True Tone technology; high brightness; and support for P3 wide color. Only the 2024 iPad Pro get the new Ultra Retina XDR display. https://www.macworld.com/article/1835319/2024-ipad-pro-release-specs-features-price.html</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new iPad Air comes in new colors: Blue and Purple, along with Starlight and Space Gray of the previous generation. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>iPad Air M2 Specs </h2>