all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Apple iPad Air sixth-gen\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1919w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-07-151028.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The new iPad Air models feature the M2, with its faster CPU, GPU, and Neural Engine compared to the M1 in the previous generation. Apple says that the new chip means the  iPad Air is “nearly 50 percent faster than the previous iPad Air with M1 for a wide range of productivity and creative tasks.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The M2 also improves on the AI capabilities, with a 16-core Neural Engine that is 40 percent faster than the M1, according t