ntenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=1536%2C854&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=2048%2C1139&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"667\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"iPad Air 2024 landscape camera\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2360w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=768%2C427&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=1200%2C667&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=1536%2C854&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=2048%2C1139&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/iPad-Air-2024-landscape-camera.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"667\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Like the 2024 iPad Pro (and the 2022 iPad) the front-facing Ultra Wide 12MP camera with Center Stage is now located along the landscape edge. This is a better position for FaceTime and other video calling apps. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The speakers have also improved, according to Apple, with the 13-inch model delivering “even better sound quality with double the bass.” </p>\n\niPad</div>","author":"","siteTitle":"Macworld","siteHash":"37e84dd5a21fa961d6d6630e269546024dbb7741b2e2fadbe74f47383c70dfbb","entryHash":"ba2639852c921354cb18994b764e9b844f731ad360e41adeff32524467c66fa8","category":"Apple"}